		"severity": "SEVERITY_MODERATE",
		"topic": "An update for xorg-x11-server, xorg-x11-server-Xwayland, and xorg-x11-xtrans-devel is now available for Rocky Linux 8.\nRocky Enterprise Software Foundation Product Security has rated this update as having a security impact of Moderate. A Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) base score, which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVE link(s) in the References section.",
